Bg4 10. h3 Bh5 11. Nf1 b5 12. Bc2 d5 13. Qe2 dxe4 14. dxe4 Bc5 15. Ng3 Bg6 16.
Nh4 {A move that has to be calculated! Here, it works well.} h6 (16... Nxe4 17.
