g2 since we castle immediately and protect the g2-pawn.} c6 (5... Bc5 6. d3 c6
7. Bc4 Ne7 (7... d6 8. Nd2 Ne7 9. Qh5 {When the knight is on e7, this can be
an annoying move for Black, although of course, White isn't obliged to play it.
