{This is a great positional game by the Greek Grandmaster.} 1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6
3. Bb5 a6 4. Ba4 d6 5. c3 Bd7 6. O-O g6 7. d4 Bg7 8. h3 Nge7 $2 9. dxe5 $1 Nxe5
10. Nxe5 dxe5 11. Be3 (11. Qxd7+ $6 Qxd7 12. Bxd7+ Kxd7 13. Rd1+ Ke6 $11) 11...
Bxa4 (11... b5 $2 12. Bb3 $16) 12. Qxa4+ Qd7 13. Qb3 $1 {We don't exchange the
queens when Black's king is in the center! We may offer a queen exchange again
after Black castles short.} (13. Qxd7+ Kxd7 14. Rd1+ Ke6 $11) 13... Qc6 14. Nd2
O-O 15. a4 a5 $2 (15... Nc8 $1 16. Qd5 (16. a5 $5) 16... Qxd5 17. exd5 $14) 16.
Rfd1 (16. Qc4 $5 $14) 16... b6 $6 (16... Rfd8 17. Qb5 $14 (17. Qc4 $4 Rxd2 $19)
) 17. Qc4 $1 Rfd8 $6 (17... Qb7 18. Nf3 Rfd8 $2 19. Ng5 $18) 18. Qxc6 (18. f3
$4 Rxd2 $19) 18... Nxc6 19. Nc4 Kf8 $2 (19... Rxd1+ 20. Rxd1 Rd8 21. Rxd8+ $1 (
21. Rb1 $5 f5 22. f3 Kf7 23. Kf1 Ke6 24. Ke2 $14) (21. Rd5 $5 Kf8 22. f4 $14)
21... Nxd8 22. b4 axb4 23. cxb4 Bf8 24. a5 b5 (24... Bxb4 25. a6 Nc6 26. Nxe5
Na7 27. Nd7 Ba5 28. e5 c5 29. Kf1 c4 30. Ke2 $18) 25. a6 Nc6 26. Nxe5 $18) 20.
g4 $5 Rxd1+ 21. Rxd1 Rd8 22. Rxd8+ (22. Rb1 $5) 22... Nxd8 23. b4 axb4 24. cxb4
Nc6 25. b5 Nd4 26. Kf1 Ke7 27. Bxd4 exd4 28. Ke2 f5 29. exf5 gxf5 30. gxf5 Kf6
31. Nd6 $1 Bf8 (31... Ke7 32. Ne4 $18) 32. Ne8+ Kxf5 33. Nxc7 Ke4 34. f3+ Ke5
35. Kd3 Bd6 36. f4+ Kf5 37. Nd5 Bc5 38. Kc4 d3 39. a5 1-0

