1. e4 Nc6 2. Nf3 e5 3. Bb5 a6 4. Ba4 g6 5. d4 b5 6. Bb3 exd4 (6... Bg7 7. dxe5
Nxe5 8. Nxe5 Bxe5 9. Qd5 $18 (9. Bxf7+ {This is also winning but 9.Qd5 is even
