Nd2 {Even with a slightly different move order, we ended up in the same
position.}) 14. bxa5 Qxa5 15. b4 {This active approach seems very good for
White.} Qh5 16. Na3 O-O 17. Bb2 Nc6 18. Qd2 Bb7 19. Bd5 Rab8 20. b5 axb5 21.
Nxb5 Ba6 22. Ba3 Rfe8 23. Rfb1 Ne5 24. Qf4 Bh6 25. Qg3 Bxb5 26. axb5 Rb6 27. h3
