Archangelsk, it's instructive to note how White develops the advantage after
the pawn push c4! Also, the games in which the arising positions are with
doubled pawns after} 7. O-O Bc5 8. Be3 Bxe3 9. fxe3 {illustrate quite well 
how the game can develop.} *

