because it also restricts that bishop.} (7. d4 {In this particular move order,
this option may be possible too.}) 7... Be7 8. c4 O-O (8... bxc4 9. Bxc4 O-O
10. Nc3 {Transposes to the game.}) (8... b4 9. Ba4 d6 10. a3 $14 (10. h3 O-O
