1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 Nf6 4. d3 Bc5 5. O-O Nd4 6. Be3 Nxf3+ 7. Qxf3 Bxe3
8. Qxe3 O-O 9. Bc4 c6 10. Bb3 d6 11. f4 Qb6 12. Qxb6 axb6 13. fxe5 dxe5 14. Nd2
b5 15. Nf3 Re8 (15... Nd7 16. Ng5 Nf6 {Black is stuck.}) 16. Ng5 Re7 17. a3 $1
(17. Nxf7 $3 {The standard tactic we have seen before in the theory section.}
Rxf7 18. d4 $1 exd4 (18... c5 19. Bxf7+ Kxf7 20. dxe5) 19. Bxf7+ (19. e5 Nd5 {
dont allow this!}) 19... Kxf7 20. e5 {winning material.}) 17... h6 18. Nxf7
Rxf7 19. d4 exd4 20. Bxf7+ Kxf7 21. e5 c5 22. exf6 gxf6 23. Rae1 b6 24. Rf4 Be6
25. Rfe4 Bf5 26. Re7+ Kg6 27. R1e2 Rd8 28. h3 h5 29. Rb7 Rd6 30. Kf2 c4 31. Kg3
d3 32. cxd3 cxd3 33. Rd2 Rc6 34. Kf4 Rc4+ 35. Ke3 Re4+ 36. Kf3 Re6 37. Rc7 Be4+
38. Kf2 Bf5 39. Rc1 Rd6 40. Re1 Rd4 41. Re3 Rc4 42. Re7 Rc6 43. Ke3 Rd6 44. g4
hxg4 45. hxg4 Bxg4 46. Rxd3 Rc6 47. Rc3 Rd6 48. Kf4 f5 49. Ke5 Rf6 50. Rcc7 1-0

