need?}) 11... f5 12. exf5 gxf5 13. dxe5 dxe5 14. Bc5 {White wins material.})
10. Bg5 (10. Be3 {is also possible.}) 10... b5 11. Bc2 Bb7 12. Nbd2 Nb8 13. Nf1
(13. b4 Nbd7 14. a4 {White has good space.}) 13... Nbd7 14. Ne3 c5 15. Nd2 Qc7
