{An amazing performance by Caruana !!} 1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 a6 4. Ba4 Nf6
5. d3 b5 6. Bb3 Bc5 7. c3 d6 (7... h6 $2 8. d4 exd4 9. e5 $18 {White is
winning.}) 8. Bg5 h6 9. Bh4 Ba7 10. O-O Na5 $6 (10... Qe7 {Black is next
intending g5.} 11. a4 g5 12. Bg3 h5 13. h4 g4 14. Ng5 Nd8 15. axb5 axb5 16. Na3
c6 17. d4 Nd7 18. d5 Nc5 19. dxc6 f6 20. Nxb5 fxg5 21. c7 {These crazy
complications finally work well for White.}) 11. Bc2 g5 12. Bg3 Nh5 13. a4 Nxg3
14. hxg3 Nc6 15. axb5 axb5 16. Na3 Ba6 (16... Rb8 17. Nxb5 Rxb5 18. Ba4 Ba6 (
18... Rb6 19. Bxc6+ Rxc6 20. Rxa7 {The endgame is better for White.}) 19. Bxb5
Bxb5 20. c4 {Winning material and soon the game.}) 17. Bb3 Ne7 18. d4 exd4 19.
Nxd4 $1 b4 20. Nc4 Bxc4 21. Bxc4 O-O 22. cxb4 d5 23. exd5 Qd6 24. Nb5 Qxb4 25.
b3 Qc5 26. Qf3 Kg7 27. Ra6 f6 28. Rfa1 Nc8 29. Kh2 1-0

